Stupid clock ideas

Child mathmatics learning clock
-difficulty levels
-learns from experience
-multiple inputs and higher difficulties
-multiple choice and lower difficulties/ pure input at higher difficulties

*design ideas/problems

create varied mathmatical problems from a given solution

case 1 addition =
rand int (1-12), save x, minus randINT from current time, save result y,  
what is x + y?
case 2 subtraction =
addition reversed
case 3 Multiplication =
divide by random int x between 2-12, exitloop if answer y equals whole number
what is x * y?

reminder to set reminder clock
-reminds to move
-reminds to set reminders at the end of the day
-reminds you to sleep/wake

